trans-unit.source: Serves as the base class for all Web Parts part controls, which render a modular user interface on a Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som basisklasse for alle webdeler Delkontroller som gjengir moduler brukergrensesnitt på en side for Web-skjemaer.

trans-unit.source: The Part class defines properties that are common to all part controls and enable them to have a modular and consistent appearance on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Del klassen definerer egenskaper som er felles for alle Delkontroller og aktivere dem med et moduler og konsekvent utseende på en webside.

trans-unit.source: These common properties include a title, a description, and characteristics of the chrome or frame that surrounds a part control.
trans-unit.target: Disse felles egenskapene inkluderer en tittel, en beskrivelse og egenskaper i chrome eller rammen som omgir en del-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A> property specifies a title for the part control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>egenskapen angir en tittel for kontrollen som en del.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A> property is used to summarize the part control's purpose, and appears as a ToolTip in the title bar of the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>egenskapen brukes til å lage et sammendrag del kontrollens formålet og vises som et verktøytips i tittellinjen i kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A> property dictates what kind of border is rendered around a part control, while the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A> property indicates whether a part control is rendered normally, or minimized.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A>egenskapen fastsetter hva slags kantlinje gjengis rundt en del kontroll mens den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A>egenskapen angir om en del kontroll er gjengis vanligvis eller minimert.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The border of a part control is affected by the properties of the zone that contains it; for example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A> property affects the frames of all part controls contained in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Kantlinjen på en del kontroll påvirkes av egenskaper for sonen som inneholder den. for eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A>påvirker forhandleren for alle Delkontroller i en sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: One type of part control is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, which renders content inside a corresponding zone.
trans-unit.target: En type del kontroll er den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen, som gjengir innholdet i en tilsvarende sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Another type is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control, which provides user interface (UI) controls used to modify (personalize) individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: En annen type er den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollen, som gir brukeren brukergrensesnittet (UI) kontroller som brukes til å endre (tilpassing) individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: A third type of part control is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, which provides a list of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls that users can add to or remove from a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Er et tredje kontrolltypen som en del av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen, som gir en oversikt over <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller som brukere kan legges til eller fjernes fra en webside.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Part controls are contained in zones, all of which derive from the abstract <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone> class.
trans-unit.target: Del kontrollene er plassert i soner alle avledes fra abstrakt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>

trans-unit.source: A zone is responsible for organizing the part controls it contains.
trans-unit.target: En sone er ansvarlig for organisering av del kontrollene den inneholder.

trans-unit.source: Each zone also renders UI elements for itself, including a header, a footer, a title bar, and UI elements around each contained part control, such as borders.
trans-unit.target: Hver sone også gjengir UI-elementene for seg selv, inkludert en topptekst, bunntekst, en tittellinjen og UI-elementene rundt hver inneholder del kontroll, for eksempel kantlinjer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > While part controls usually reside in zones, it is possible to place a part control outside a zone, if the control is referenced declaratively in the markup of a Web page.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Selv Delkontroller ligger vanligvis i soner, er det mulig å plassere en del kontroll utenfor en sone Hvis kontrollen deklarativt koden for en webside.

trans-unit.source: If a part control is declared outside a zone on a Web page, the control still works, but loses most of its Web Parts functionality.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en del kontroll er deklarert utenfor en sone på en side, kontrollen fortsatt fungerer, men mister de fleste av webdeler funksjonaliteten.

trans-unit.source: For example, the control cannot be edited, and cannot be dragged into a zone at run time.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel kontrollen kan ikke redigeres, og du kan dra til en sone på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: It is also helpful to remember that no part control can be dragged from a zone and dropped onto a page outside of a zone at run time.
trans-unit.target: Det er også nyttig å huske at ingen deler kan drar fra en sone og slippes på en side utenfor en sone på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Some examples of base part types, and their corresponding zone types, are shown in the following table.
trans-unit.target: Noen eksempler på base del typer, og de tilsvarende typene sone vises i følgende tabell.

trans-unit.source: |Part control type|Zone type| |-----------------------|---------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>| The various kinds of part controls that derive from the Part class handle the inherited, UI-oriented properties differently.
trans-unit.target: | Del kontrolltypen | Sone typen | |-----------------------|---------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>| Forskjellige typer Delkontroller som er avledet fra klassen del håndtere egenskapene arvede, UI-orientert annerledes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls override several of the inherited UI properties, and mark them with the `Personalizable` attribute (for details, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute> class documentation), which enables the values of those properties to be saved for future browser sessions, a feature known as personalization.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller eller flere av egenskapene for arvede Brukergrensesnittet og merke dem med den `Personalizable` attributtet (Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute>klasse dokumentasjonen), som aktiverer verdiene for disse egenskapene lagres for fremtidige nettleseren økter en funksjon kalt personlige data.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you programmatically enable a user to update the value of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Title%2A> property at run time, that value will be personalized (assuming that personalization is enabled, which is the default).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du aktiverer en bruker til å oppdatere verdien for et program for eksempel en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Title%2A>egenskapen ved kjøretid, som verdien skal være tilpasset (forutsatt at tilpassing er aktivert, som er standard).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Title%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Several UI properties that <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls inherit from the Part class, and from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> class, are handled the same way.
trans-unit.target: Flere egenskaper i Brukergrensesnittet som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller arver fra en del klassen og fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>klasse, behandles på samme måte.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In contrast, other part controls, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>, do not enable the inherited UI properties to be personalized.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning andre del kontrollerer, slik som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>, aktiverer du ikke arvede UI-egenskapene for å tilpasses.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: For this reason, programmatically assigned property values are not saved for future browser sessions.
trans-unit.target: Derfor tilordnet programmatisk egenskapen ikke lagres verdiene for fremtidige nettleseren økter.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you programmatically enable a user to update a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart.Title%2A> property at run time, the updated value is lost after the control is closed or the browser session ends.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du aktiverer programmatisk gjelder for eksempel en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart.Title%2A>-egenskapen ved kjøretid, den oppdaterte verdien går tapt når kontrollen er lukket eller nettleseren økten avsluttes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart.Title%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An easy way to save the values on such inherited UI properties for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls for future browser sessions is to declare the property values in page persistence format.
trans-unit.target: En enkel måte å lagre verdiene for eksempel arvet Brukergrensesnittet egenskaper for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller for fremtidige nettleseren økter er deklarere egenskapsverdier på sider utholdenhet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: However, this is a static approach and still does not allow users to personalize the property values.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en statisk tilnærming imidlertid og fortsatt tillater ikke brukerne å tilpasse egenskapsverdiene.

trans-unit.source: As an alternative, if you want to enable programmatic updates to the inherited UI properties so users can personalize them at run time, you can use private, static variables to save the property values.
trans-unit.target: Som et alternativ hvis du vil aktivere programmatisk oppdateringer for egenskapene arvede Brukergrensesnittet slik at brukere kan tilpasse dem ved kjøretid, kan du bruke private, statiske variabler lagre egenskapsverdiene.

trans-unit.source: Each time a new instance of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is created (for example, in the method that handles the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init> event), you can reassign a static variable's value to a corresponding property.
trans-unit.target: Hver gang en ny forekomst av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen er opprettet (for eksempel i metoden som behandler kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init>hendelsen), kan du tilordne en statisk variabelverdien til en tilsvarende egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Such an approach gives users the ability to personalize the editing UI and catalog UI of a Web Parts application.
trans-unit.target: En slik tilnærming gir brukerne muligheten til å tilpasse redigering Brukergrensesnittet og katalogen Brukergrensesnittet for et webdeler-program.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether a part control is in a minimized or normal state.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir om det er en del kontroll minimert eller normal tilstanden.

trans-unit.source: A part control's ChromeState can be normal or minimized.
trans-unit.target: En del kontroll ChromeState kan være normal eller minimert.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The value specified is not one of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte verdien er ikke én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeState"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of border that frames a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir kantlinjetypen som rammer en webdeler-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A part control's ChromeType property determines what kind of border surrounds the control.
trans-unit.target: En del kontroll ChromeType egenskapen bestemmer hvilken type kantlinje omgir kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Options include showing a title only, a border only, a title and border, neither, or the default option, which simply uses the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Alternativene omfatter viser bare tittelen, bare en kantlinje, en tittel og kantlinje, verken, eller standardalternativet, som bruker ganske enkelt verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er ikke én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PartChromeType"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object that contains the child controls for a specified server control in the user interface hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder underordnede kontroller for en angitt serverkontroll i grensesnittet brukerhierarkiet.

trans-unit.source: On an ASP.NET page, when controls are added declaratively between the opening and closing tags of a server control, ASP.NET automatically adds the controls to the containing server control's <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: På en ASP.NET-side når kontrollene er lagt til mellom innledende og avsluttende koder på en serverkontroll på deklarativt ASP.NET automatisk legger til kontrollene i den inneholdende serverkontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: Any HTML tags or text strings that are not processed on the server are treated as <xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl> objects.
trans-unit.target: Et HTML-koder eller tekststrenger som ikke er behandlet på serveren, behandles som <xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl>

trans-unit.source: These are added to the collection like other server controls.
trans-unit.target: Disse er lagt til samlingen som andre serverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> property allows you programmatic access to the instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection> class for any server control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>egenskapen kan du programmatisk tilgang til forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>klasse for alle serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can add controls to the collection, remove controls from the collection, or iterate through the server controls in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til kontroller i samlingen, Fjern kontroller fra samlingen, eller gå gjennom serverkontroller i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The collection of child controls for the specified server control.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av underordnede kontroller for den angitte serverkontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Binds a data source to the invoked server control and all its child controls.
trans-unit.target: En datakilde, bindes til startet serverkontroll og alle underordnede kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a brief phrase that summarizes what the part control does, for use in ToolTips and catalogs of part controls.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et kort uttrykk som summerer det del kontrollen gjør, for bruk i verktøytips og kataloger del kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The Description property is typically a string that is used in catalogs that provide lists of part controls, and as a ToolTip in the part control's title bar.
trans-unit.target: Description-egenskapen er vanligvis en streng som brukes i kataloger som gir lister med Delkontroller, og som et verktøytips del kontrollens tittellinjen.

trans-unit.source: The content of the Description appears in a ToolTip when you position your mouse pointer over the title text in a part control's title bar.
trans-unit.target: Innholdet i beskrivelsen vises i et verktøytips når du plasserer musepekeren over tittelteksten i tittellinjen i en del-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The ToolTip text is created from the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A> property, followed by a hyphen, followed by the Description property value.
trans-unit.target: Teksten for verktøytipset er opprettet fra verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>egenskapen, etterfulgt av en bindestrek, etterfulgt av egenskapsverdien beskrivelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen Hvis du velger, kan lagres automatisk på en ressursfil ved hjelp av en designer verktøyet.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> and [Globalization and Localization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute>og [globalisering og lokalisering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: A string that briefly summarizes the part control's functionality.
trans-unit.target: En streng som kort oppsummerer del kontrollens funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Allows the developer of a designer for a composite part control to recreate the control's child controls on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Tillater at utvikleren av en designer for en sammensatt del kontroll til å gjenopprette kontrollens underordnede kontroller på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the title of a part control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tittelen på en del-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The visible title text in a part control's title bar is set by the Title property.
trans-unit.target: Synlig tittelteksten i delen kontrollens tittellinjen er angitt av egenskapen tittel.

trans-unit.source: The title text also appears as part of the ToolTip text when you position your mouse pointer over the title bar of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control or other server control that appears in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zone.
trans-unit.target: Tittelteksten også ser ut som en del av Verktøytipsteksten når du plasserer musepekeren over tittellinjen i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll eller andre serverkontroll som vises i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The style of the title text is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A> property of the zone that contains the part control.
trans-unit.target: Stilen på tittelteksten fastsettes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A>for sonen som inneholder deler kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not supply a title for a control, the Web Parts control set automatically calculates a default string to use as a title.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en tittel for en kontroll, beregner webdeler kontrollen automatisk en standardstrengen som skal brukes som en tittel.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Also, it is possible to provide a standard subtitle that is appended to the title string.
trans-unit.target: Det er også mulig å angi en standard undertittel som skal legges til en tittel-streng.

trans-unit.source: For details, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Subtitle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Subtitle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Subtitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen Hvis du velger, kan lagres automatisk på en ressursfil ved hjelp av en designer verktøyet.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> and [Globalization and Localization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute>og [globalisering og lokalisering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the title of the part control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer tittelen kontrollens del.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").
